      <td>平调</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>/</td>
      <td>停顿</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<blockquote>
  <p>Example:
A l<strong>o</strong>t_of p<strong>eo</strong>ple ask me&gt; if_it’s p<strong>o</strong>ssible˄ to s<strong>oun</strong>d like_a n<strong>at</strong>ive sp<strong>ea</strong>ker.
